Package client.gamestate

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DiscardingState
    This state represents the gameState when a player is discarding cards due to the robber
    FirstRoundState
    class to represent the game state during the first round of play
    GameState
    The abstract class of states the player and game is in.
    IsNotTurnState
    class that represents the gameState when the player is waiting for other players to play - its not the players turn
    PlayingState
    class to represent the gameState when it is the player's turn and they can play
    RobbingState
    class to represent the gameState when a player is robbing
    RollingState
    game state to represent when the player is rolling
    SecondRoundState
    class to represent the game state during the second round of play
